      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Jo Farrar became the chief executive of HM Prison & Probation Service in April 2019. Jo came to this role from Local Government and Public Services, where she held the position of Director General .</p>

<h2 id="career">Career</h2>

<p>Before her role at <abbr title="Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government">MHCLG</abbr>, Jo was Chief Executive of Bath and North East Somerset Council.</p>

<p>Prior to her career in local government she had a strong background in the Civil Service, with roles at the Department for Work and Pensions, the Home Office and the Cabinet Office.</p>

</div>
      </section>

